The paper deals with handwriting recognition using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research. The paper also involves object detection using neural networks, which falls under computer vision. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and long short term memory (LSTM) networks for feature extraction and recognition respectively, are common techniques in natural language processing (cs.CL) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI) research. Therefore, these five sub-categories are the most likely for this paper.
